{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01LXnhHPD8SB59QbdVn9ck1Z","type":"tool_result","content":"   200ŌåÆ    totalVolumeLamports: string,\n   201ŌåÆ    totalEarnedLamports: string,\n   202ŌåÆ    pendingLamports: string\n   203ŌåÆ  }\n   204ŌåÆ\n   205ŌåÆGET  /referral/earnings            ŌĆö Get detailed per-game earnings log\n   206ŌåÆ  Query: { page?: number, limit?: number }\n   207ŌåÆ  Response: {\n   208ŌåÆ    items: [{\n   209ŌåÆ      roundId: string,\n   210ŌåÆ      gameType: string,\n   211ŌåÆ      refereeWallet: string,\n   212ŌåÆ      wagerLamports: string,\n   213ŌåÆ      earnedLamports: string,\n   214ŌåÆ      createdAt: string\n   215ŌåÆ    }],\n   216ŌåÆ    pagination: { page: number, totalPages: number }\n   217ŌåÆ  }\n   218ŌåÆ\n   219ŌåÆPOST /referral/claim               ŌĆö Request earnings claim (async via queue)\n   220ŌåÆ  Response: { claimId: string, amountLamports: string, status: \"pending\" }\n   221ŌåÆ\n   222ŌåÆGET  /referral/claim/:claimId      ŌĆö Poll claim status\n   223ŌåÆ  Response: { claimId: string, amountLamports: string, status: \"pending\" | \"completed\" | \"failed\", txSignature?: string }\n   224ŌåÆ```\n   225ŌåÆ\n   226ŌåÆ**Acceptance Criteria:**\n   227ŌåÆ- [ ] All endpoints require JWT authentication <!-- gap: no referral routes registered -->\n   228ŌåÆ- [ ] All endpoints return appropriate error codes (400 for bad input, 404 for not found, 409 for conflict) <!-- gap: no referral routes -->\n   229ŌåÆ- [ ] Rate limiting is applied to code generation and claim endpoints <!-- gap: no referral routes -->\n   230ŌåÆ- [ ] Monetary values use lamport strings (not floating point) <!-- gap: no API responses to verify -->\n   231ŌåÆ\n   232ŌåÆ### FR-8: Database Schema\n   233ŌåÆ\n   234ŌåÆNew tables for the referral system. All off-chain, no program changes.\n   235ŌåÆ\n   236ŌåÆ```sql\n   237ŌåÆreferral_codes (\n   238ŌåÆ  id            SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,\n   239ŌåÆ  wallet        TEXT NOT NULL UNIQUE,\n   240ŌåÆ  code          TEXT NOT NULL UNIQUE,   -- player-chosen, 3-16 chars [a-z0-9-]\n   241ŌåÆ  created_at    TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT now(),\n   242ŌåÆ  updated_at    TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT now()\n   243ŌåÆ)\n   244ŌåÆ\n   245ŌåÆreferral_links (\n   246ŌåÆ  id              SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,\n   247ŌåÆ  referrer_wallet TEXT NOT NULL,\n   248ŌåÆ  referee_wallet  TEXT NOT NULL UNIQUE,  -- one referrer per player\n   249ŌåÆ  created_at      TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT now()\n   250ŌåÆ)\n   251ŌåÆ\n   252ŌåÆreferral_earnings (\n   253ŌåÆ  id                        SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,\n   254ŌåÆ  referrer_wallet           TEXT NOT NULL,\n   255ŌåÆ  referee_wallet            TEXT NOT NULL,\n   256ŌåÆ  round_id                  TEXT NOT NULL,\n   257ŌåÆ  game_type                 TEXT NOT NULL,\n   258ŌåÆ  wager_lamports            BIGINT NOT NULL,\n   259ŌåÆ  fee_lamports              BIGINT NOT NULL,\n   260ŌåÆ  referrer_earned_lamports  BIGINT NOT NULL,\n   261ŌåÆ  referrer_rate_bps         INTEGER NOT NULL,\n   262ŌåÆ  referee_rebate_lamports   BIGINT NOT NULL,\n   263ŌåÆ  referee_rebate_rate_bps   INTEGER NOT NULL,  -- always 1000 for v1\n   264ŌåÆ  created_at                TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT now(),\n   265ŌåÆ  UNIQUE (referee_wallet, round_id)  -- idempotency: one earning per player per round\n   266ŌåÆ)\n   267ŌåÆ\n   268ŌåÆreferral_claims (\n   269ŌåÆ  id                UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid(),\n   270ŌåÆ  wallet            TEXT NOT NULL,\n   271ŌåÆ  amount_lamports   BIGINT NOT NULL,\n   272ŌåÆ  status            TEXT NOT NULL CHECK (status IN ('pending','processing','completed','failed')),\n   273ŌåÆ  tx_signature      TEXT,\n   274ŌåÆ  error             TEXT,\n   275ŌåÆ  requested_at      TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT now(),\n   276ŌåÆ  processed_at      TIMESTAMPTZ\n   277ŌåÆ)\n   278ŌåÆ\n   279ŌåÆ-- KOL custom referrer rates (overrides default 1000 bps)\n   280ŌåÆreferral_kol_rates (\n   281ŌåÆ  wallet          TEXT PRIMARY KEY,\n   282ŌåÆ  rate_bps        INTEGER NOT NULL,  -- e.g., 2000 = 20% of total fee (= 100 bps of wager)\n   283ŌåÆ  set_by          TEXT NOT NULL,     -- admin wallet\n   284ŌåÆ  created_at      TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT now(),\n   285ŌåÆ  updated_at      TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT now()\n   286ŌåÆ)\n   287ŌåÆ```\n   288ŌåÆ\n   289ŌåÆ**Acceptance Criteria:**\n   290ŌåÆ- [x] All tables created via migration (referral_codes, referral_links, referral_earnings, referral_claims, referral_kol_rates) <!-- satisfied: 011_referral.sql creates all 5 tables -->\n   291ŌåÆ- [x] `referral_links.referee_wallet` has UNIQUE constraint (one referrer per player) <!-- satisfied: 011_referral.sql:22 ŌĆö referee_wallet TEXT NOT NULL UNIQUE -->\n   292ŌåÆ- [x] `referral_codes.code` has UNIQUE constraint <!-- satisfied: 011_referral.sql:12 ŌĆö code TEXT NOT NULL UNIQUE -->\n   293ŌåÆ- [x] Appropriate indexes on wallet columns and `referral_earnings.round_id` <!-- satisfied: 011_referral.sql ŌĆö 6 indexes covering all wallet lookups and round_id -->\n   294ŌåÆ- [x] `referral_earnings` has unique idempotency guard (`UNIQUE (referee_wallet, round_id)`) <!-- satisfied: 011_referral.sql:43-44 ŌĆö CONSTRAINT uq_referral_earnings_referee_round -->\n   295ŌåÆ- [x] `referral_claims.status` constrained to `pending|processing|completed|failed` <!-- satisfied: 011_referral.sql:67-68 ŌĆö CHECK constraint chk_referral_claims_status -->\n   296ŌåÆ\n   297ŌåÆ### FR-9: Frontend ŌĆö Routes, Pages, and Components\n   298ŌåÆ\n   299ŌåÆAll frontend changes live in `apps/platform/`. Follows existing patterns: React Router routes in `App.tsx`, NavLink in `Sidebar.tsx`, feature code in `features/referral/`, API wrappers in `lib/referral-api.ts`.\n   300ŌåÆ\n   301ŌåÆ#### 9a. New Route: `/r/:code` ŌĆö Referral Link Handler\n   302ŌåÆ\n   303ŌåÆA lightweight route that captures the referral code from the URL, persists it, and redirects to the home page (or wherever the player was headed).\n   304ŌåÆ\n   305ŌåÆ**Flow:**\n   306ŌåÆ1. Player visits `taunt.bet/r/my-code`\n   307ŌåÆ2. Route component reads `:code` via `useParams()`\n   308ŌåÆ3. Stores `{ code, capturedAt }` in `localStorage` key `referral_code`\n   309ŌåÆ4. Redirects to `/` via `<Navigate to=\"/\" replace />`\n   310ŌåÆ5. On next authentication (in `SessionContext` or a dedicated `useReferralApply` hook), if `referral_code` exists in localStorage and user has no referrer ŌåÆ calls `POST /referral/apply` ŌåÆ clears localStorage on success\n   311ŌåÆ\n   312ŌåÆ**Acceptance Criteria:**\n   313ŌåÆ- [ ] Route `/r/:code` registered in `App.tsx` <!-- gap: not in App.tsx routes -->\n   314ŌåÆ- [ ] Code stored in localStorage on visit (no auth required) <!-- gap: no localStorage referral code logic -->\n   315ŌåÆ- [ ] Redirect to `/` happens immediately after capture <!-- gap: no route handler -->\n   316ŌåÆ- [ ] On successful authentication, stored code is applied via API <!-- gap: no useReferralApply hook -->\n   317ŌåÆ- [ ] localStorage is cleared after successful apply (or if code is invalid/already linked) <!-- gap: no apply logic -->\n   318ŌåÆ- [ ] Invalid/expired codes show a toast notification, not a blocking error <!-- gap: no error handling -->\n   319ŌåÆ\n   320ŌåÆ#### 9b. Sidebar Navigation ŌĆö Referrals Link\n   321ŌåÆ\n   322ŌåÆNew nav item in the \"Player\" section of `Sidebar.tsx`, between \"Quests\" and the \"Platform\" section.\n   323ŌåÆ\n   324ŌåÆ```tsx\n   325ŌåÆ<NavLink to=\"/referrals\" className={({ isActive }) => `nv-item ${isActive ? \"active\" : \"\"}`}\n   326ŌåÆ  style={{ \"--nc\": \"var(--color-green)\" } as React.CSSProperties}>\n   327ŌåÆ  <div className=\"nv-ico\">\n   328ŌåÆ    {/* share/link icon */}\n   329ŌåÆ  </div>\n   330ŌåÆ  <span className=\"nv-lbl\">Referrals</span>\n   331ŌåÆ</NavLink>\n   332ŌåÆ```\n   333ŌåÆ\n   334ŌåÆ**Acceptance Criteria:**\n   335ŌåÆ- [ ] \"Referrals\" nav item appears in sidebar under \"Player\" section <!-- gap: not in Sidebar.tsx -->\n   336ŌåÆ- [ ] Active state styling matches existing nav items <!-- gap: not implemented -->\n   337ŌåÆ- [ ] Icon is a share/link-style SVG consistent with sidebar icon style <!-- gap: not implemented -->\n   338ŌåÆ- [ ] Navigates to `/referrals` <!-- gap: not implemented -->\n   339ŌåÆ\n   340ŌåÆ#### 9c. Referral Page (`/referrals`)\n   341ŌåÆ\n   342ŌåÆMain referral hub page at route `/referrals`. Requires wallet connection + authentication. Shows different states based on whether the player has generated a code yet.\n   343ŌåÆ\n   344ŌåÆ**Layout ŌĆö top to bottom:**\n   345ŌåÆ\n   346ŌåÆ1. **Your Referral Link** (card)\n   347ŌåÆ   - If no code yet: input field to choose a custom code (3-16 chars, `[a-z0-9-]`) + \"Set Code\" button ŌåÆ calls `POST /referral/code { code: \"...\" }` ŌåÆ shows link\n   348ŌåÆ   - If code exists: display code + full URL in a styled input/box with a **Copy Link** button\n   349ŌåÆ   - Copy uses `navigator.clipboard.writeText(url)` with a brief \"Copied!\" feedback (tooltip or button text swap)"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"e3b67986-fd78-4b1a-b5f8-3ba5e0f9fe3d","uuid":"a178f9b3-c82b-4b34-ac0c-6d5a0f8955bf","timestamp":"2026-03-25T12:18:03.474Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/workspaces/rng-utopia/docs/specs/300-referral-system/spec.md","content":"    totalVolumeLamports: string,\n    totalEarnedLamports: string,\n    pendingLamports: string\n  }\n\nGET  /referral/earnings            ŌĆö Get detailed per-game earnings log\n  Query: { page?: number, limit?: number }\n  Response: {\n    items: [{\n      roundId: string,\n      gameType: string,\n      refereeWallet: string,\n      wagerLamports: string,\n      earnedLamports: string,\n      createdAt: string\n    }],\n    pagination: { page: number, totalPages: number }\n  }\n\nPOST /referral/claim               ŌĆö Request earnings claim (async via queue)\n  Response: { claimId: string, amountLamports: string, status: \"pending\" }\n\nGET  /referral/claim/:claimId      ŌĆö Poll claim status\n  Response: { claimId: string, amountLamports: string, status: \"pending\" | \"completed\" | \"failed\", txSignature?: string }\n```\n\n**Acceptance Criteria:**\n- [ ] All endpoints require JWT authentication <!-- gap: no referral routes registered -->\n- [ ] All endpoints return appropriate error codes (400 for bad input, 404 for not found, 409 for conflict) <!-- gap: no referral routes -->\n- [ ] Rate limiting is applied to code generation and claim endpoints <!-- gap: no referral routes -->\n- [ ] Monetary values use lamport strings (not floating point) <!-- gap: no API responses to verify -->\n\n### FR-8: Database Schema\n\nNew tables for the referral system. All off-chain, no program changes.\n\n```sql\nreferral_codes (\n  id            SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,\n  wallet        TEXT NOT NULL UNIQUE,\n  code          TEXT NOT NULL UNIQUE,   -- player-chosen, 3-16 chars [a-z0-9-]\n  created_at    TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT now(),\n  updated_at    TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT now()\n)\n\nreferral_links (\n  id              SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,\n  referrer_wallet TEXT NOT NULL,\n  referee_wallet  TEXT NOT NULL UNIQUE,  -- one referrer per player\n  created_at      TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT now()\n)\n\nreferral_earnings (\n  id                        SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,\n  referrer_wallet           TEXT NOT NULL,\n  referee_wallet            TEXT NOT NULL,\n  round_id                  TEXT NOT NULL,\n  game_type                 TEXT NOT NULL,\n  wager_lamports            BIGINT NOT NULL,\n  fee_lamports              BIGINT NOT NULL,\n  referrer_earned_lamports  BIGINT NOT NULL,\n  referrer_rate_bps         INTEGER NOT NULL,\n  referee_rebate_lamports   BIGINT NOT NULL,\n  referee_rebate_rate_bps   INTEGER NOT NULL,  -- always 1000 for v1\n  created_at                TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT now(),\n  UNIQUE (referee_wallet, round_id)  -- idempotency: one earning per player per round\n)\n\nreferral_claims (\n  id                UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid(),\n  wallet            TEXT NOT NULL,\n  amount_lamports   BIGINT NOT NULL,\n  status            TEXT NOT NULL CHECK (status IN ('pending','processing','completed','failed')),\n  tx_signature      TEXT,\n  error             TEXT,\n  requested_at      TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT now(),\n  processed_at      TIMESTAMPTZ\n)\n\n-- KOL custom referrer rates (overrides default 1000 bps)\nreferral_kol_rates (\n  wallet          TEXT PRIMARY KEY,\n  rate_bps        INTEGER NOT NULL,  -- e.g., 2000 = 20% of total fee (= 100 bps of wager)\n  set_by          TEXT NOT NULL,     -- admin wallet\n  created_at      TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT now(),\n  updated_at      TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT now()\n)\n```\n\n**Acceptance Criteria:**\n- [x] All tables created via migration (referral_codes, referral_links, referral_earnings, referral_claims, referral_kol_rates) <!-- satisfied: 011_referral.sql creates all 5 tables -->\n- [x] `referral_links.referee_wallet` has UNIQUE constraint (one referrer per player) <!-- satisfied: 011_referral.sql:22 ŌĆö referee_wallet TEXT NOT NULL UNIQUE -->\n- [x] `referral_codes.code` has UNIQUE constraint <!-- satisfied: 011_referral.sql:12 ŌĆö code TEXT NOT NULL UNIQUE -->\n- [x] Appropriate indexes on wallet columns and `referral_earnings.round_id` <!-- satisfied: 011_referral.sql ŌĆö 6 indexes covering all wallet lookups and round_id -->\n- [x] `referral_earnings` has unique idempotency guard (`UNIQUE (referee_wallet, round_id)`) <!-- satisfied: 011_referral.sql:43-44 ŌĆö CONSTRAINT uq_referral_earnings_referee_round -->\n- [x] `referral_claims.status` constrained to `pending|processing|completed|failed` <!-- satisfied: 011_referral.sql:67-68 ŌĆö CHECK constraint chk_referral_claims_status -->\n\n### FR-9: Frontend ŌĆö Routes, Pages, and Components\n\nAll frontend changes live in `apps/platform/`. Follows existing patterns: React Router routes in `App.tsx`, NavLink in `Sidebar.tsx`, feature code in `features/referral/`, API wrappers in `lib/referral-api.ts`.\n\n#### 9a. New Route: `/r/:code` ŌĆö Referral Link Handler\n\nA lightweight route that captures the referral code from the URL, persists it, and redirects to the home page (or wherever the player was headed).\n\n**Flow:**\n1. Player visits `taunt.bet/r/my-code`\n2. Route component reads `:code` via `useParams()`\n3. Stores `{ code, capturedAt }` in `localStorage` key `referral_code`\n4. Redirects to `/` via `<Navigate to=\"/\" replace />`\n5. On next authentication (in `SessionContext` or a dedicated `useReferralApply` hook), if `referral_code` exists in localStorage and user has no referrer ŌåÆ calls `POST /referral/apply` ŌåÆ clears localStorage on success\n\n**Acceptance Criteria:**\n- [ ] Route `/r/:code` registered in `App.tsx` <!-- gap: not in App.tsx routes -->\n- [ ] Code stored in localStorage on visit (no auth required) <!-- gap: no localStorage referral code logic -->\n- [ ] Redirect to `/` happens immediately after capture <!-- gap: no route handler -->\n- [ ] On successful authentication, stored code is applied via API <!-- gap: no useReferralApply hook -->\n- [ ] localStorage is cleared after successful apply (or if code is invalid/already linked) <!-- gap: no apply logic -->\n- [ ] Invalid/expired codes show a toast notification, not a blocking error <!-- gap: no error handling -->\n\n#### 9b. Sidebar Navigation ŌĆö Referrals Link\n\nNew nav item in the \"Player\" section of `Sidebar.tsx`, between \"Quests\" and the \"Platform\" section.\n\n```tsx\n<NavLink to=\"/referrals\" className={({ isActive }) => `nv-item ${isActive ? \"active\" : \"\"}`}\n  style={{ \"--nc\": \"var(--color-green)\" } as React.CSSProperties}>\n  <div className=\"nv-ico\">\n    {/* share/link icon */}\n  </div>\n  <span className=\"nv-lbl\">Referrals</span>\n</NavLink>\n```\n\n**Acceptance Criteria:**\n- [ ] \"Referrals\" nav item appears in sidebar under \"Player\" section <!-- gap: not in Sidebar.tsx -->\n- [ ] Active state styling matches existing nav items <!-- gap: not implemented -->\n- [ ] Icon is a share/link-style SVG consistent with sidebar icon style <!-- gap: not implemented -->\n- [ ] Navigates to `/referrals` <!-- gap: not implemented -->\n\n#### 9c. Referral Page (`/referrals`)\n\nMain referral hub page at route `/referrals`. Requires wallet connection + authentication. Shows different states based on whether the player has generated a code yet.\n\n**Layout ŌĆö top to bottom:**\n\n1. **Your Referral Link** (card)\n   - If no code yet: input field to choose a custom code (3-16 chars, `[a-z0-9-]`) + \"Set Code\" button ŌåÆ calls `POST /referral/code { code: \"...\" }` ŌåÆ shows link\n   - If code exists: display code + full URL in a styled input/box with a **Copy Link** button\n   - Copy uses `navigator.clipboard.writeText(url)` with a brief \"Copied!\" feedback (tooltip or button text swap)","numLines":150,"startLine":200,"totalLines":715}}}
