nt flowsŌĆöcalling it in `settleMatch` with the coinflip game type and player wagers, and similarly in `settleLordRound` for the lord game type with the serialized player list.\n\nI'm also updating the `SettleTxDeps` interface to include the referral rate configuration, then passing that through the caller in index.ts so the settlement functions have access to it. I should verify the integration test handles this new dependency correctly.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1930,"cache_read_input_tokens":66974,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1930},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"e3b67986-fd78-4b1a-b5f8-3ba5e0f9fe3d","uuid":"4d768a3f-738c-4e50-95d8-759057c4921b"}
